trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the transport must ensure that the URI provided for the service to listen on is unique or can be used exactly as provided.
trans-unit.target: Angir om transport må sikre at den angitte for tjenesten URIEN ikke lytte på unik eller kan brukes nøyaktig som angitt.

trans-unit.source: The URI for the endpoint on which a service listens can be set programmatically using the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.ListenUri%2A> property and the value of the ListenUriMode for that endpoint is set using the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.ListenUriMode%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: URIEN for endepunktet for en tjeneste lytter som kan angis ved hjelp av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.ListenUri%2A>egenskapen og verdien for ListenUriMode for sluttpunktet angis ved hjelp av den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.ListenUriMode%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.ListenUriMode%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.ListenUri%2A>

trans-unit.source: The default value for <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.ListenUriMode%2A> is Explicit.

The value of these properties may also be set using the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.ServiceEndpointElement.ListenUri%2A> property and the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.ServiceEndpointElement.ListenUriMode%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for disse egenskapene kan også angis ved hjelp av den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.ServiceEndpointElement.ListenUri%2A>egenskapen og <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.ServiceEndpointElement.ListenUriMode%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.ServiceEndpointElement.ListenUriMode%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.ServiceEndpointElement.ListenUri%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the value of the ListenUriMode is set to Unique the transport is responsible for creating a unique URI.
trans-unit.target: Når verdien for ListenUriMode er satt til Unique er transport ansvarlig for å opprette en unik URI.

trans-unit.source: Different transports used by [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] generate this unique URI differently - For TCP in exclusive mode (<xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TcpTransportBindingElement.PortSharingEnabled%2A> is `false`) this means binding to a uniquely available port number.
trans-unit.target: Annen transport som brukes av [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] generere denne unike URIEN forskjellig - For TCP i eksklusiv modus (<xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TcpTransportBindingElement.PortSharingEnabled%2A> er `false`) Dette betyr binding til et unikt tilgjengelig portnummer.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TcpTransportBindingElement.PortSharingEnabled%2A>

trans-unit.source: - For TCP in port sharing mode (<xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TcpTransportBindingElement.PortSharingEnabled%2A> is `true`) and for all of the other existing [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] transports, this means appending a unique path (a GUID) to the end of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.ListenUri%2A>.
trans-unit.target: -For TCP port deling modus (<xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TcpTransportBindingElement.PortSharingEnabled%2A> er `true`) og for alle andre eksisterende [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] transport, betyr dette tilføyer en unik bane (en GUID) til slutten av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.ListenUri%2A>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.ListenUri%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TcpTransportBindingElement.PortSharingEnabled%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the value of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.ListenUriMode%2A> is set to Explicit mode, the transport uses the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.ListenUri%2A> exactly as it is provided, without modifying it to make it unique.
trans-unit.target: Når verdien for den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.ListenUriMode%2A>er satt til Explicit-modus, transport bruker den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.ListenUri%2A>nøyaktig som det er angitt, uten å endre det slik at den er unik.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.ListenUri%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.ListenUriMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: Specifies that the transport should use a transport-specific mechanism to ensure that the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.ListenUri*> is unique.
trans-unit.target: Angir at transport må bruke en transport-spesifikke mekanisme forsikre deg om at det <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.ListenUri*>er unik.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.ListenUri*>
